  <summary date="2021-09-17T16:50:48Z" status="Introduced in House">Growing Climate Solutions Act of 2020

This bill directs the Department of Agriculture to establish a voluntary program to certify technical assistance providers and third-party verifiers that assist farmers, ranchers, or private forest landowners in preventing or mitigating greenhouse gas emissions, sequestering carbon, or verifying processes described in protocols for greenhouse gas credit markets.</summary>
